  "reference_number": "CYB0081",
  "remarks": "\nRussian GRU 29155 associate Vitaly Aleksandrovich SHEVCHENKO, through his prior involvement with a GRU cyber unit, has been responsible for, engaging in, providing support for, or promoting the commissions, planning or preparation of relevant cyber activity. Such activity that SHEVCHENKO is or has been involved in undermines, or is intended to undermine, the integrity, prosperity or security of United Kingdom or a country other than the United Kingdom.\n",
